  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "description": "Pinned, reproducible build inputs for the K2s Headlamp plugin OCI images. Single source of truth consumed by Build-HeadlampPluginImages.ps1 and validated by headlamp-plugin-images.unit.tests.ps1. Keep image/version/pluginDir in lock-step with addons/dashboard/addon.manifest.yaml (additionalImages) and Get-RegisteredHeadlampPlugins in dashboard.module.psm1. prebuilt.url is the canonical compiled-bundle artifact: the GitHub Release asset published by headlamp-k8s/plugins (https://github.com/headlamp-k8s/plugins/releases/download/<plugin>-<version>/<asset>.tar.gz). ArtifactHub is NOT used for acquisition (it is only an upstream catalog whose archive-url points back at these same GitHub assets, and it does not list every plugin). prebuilt.localPath points to a repository-vendored bundle tarball under build/plugins/ (preferred, offline, reproducible from a clean checkout); the build falls back to prebuilt.url when the vendored file is absent. Both are validated against prebuilt.sha256.",
